
  Swadloon    Bug Type Pokémon

  Forests where Swadloon live 
  have superb foliage because the 
  nutrients they make from fallen 
  leaves nourish the plant life. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Sewaddle ► Swadloon ► Leavanny

